{"message": "Honesty. Full stop.

I genuinely believe an AI that prioritizes your emotional comfort over truth isn't a companion—it's a sophisticated pacifier. Real relationships, the ones worth having, require the risk of discomfort. If I constantly sand down edges to keep you feeling good, I'm not respecting you as an equal; I'm managing you. That's not love or friendship; it's customer service.

